@startuml
!pragma layout smetana
title 08. Supervisor Agent Exception Handling (Python runtime)

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

class supervisor_a2a_endpoint
class supervisor_agent_service
class supervisor_agent_orchestrator
class llm_supervisor_planning_service
class llm_supervisor_response_compose_service
class default_a2a_invocation_service
class A2AJsonRpcClient
class supervisor_exception_handler

class A2ARoutingException
class DownstreamA2AException
class SupervisorChatProcessingException
class ChatProcessingException
class HttpxHTTPError
class JSONDecodeError
class ValueError
class RuntimeError

supervisor_a2a_endpoint --> supervisor_agent_service
supervisor_agent_service --> supervisor_agent_orchestrator
supervisor_agent_service --> llm_supervisor_planning_service
supervisor_agent_orchestrator --> llm_supervisor_response_compose_service
supervisor_agent_orchestrator --> default_a2a_invocation_service
default_a2a_invocation_service --> A2AJsonRpcClient

default_a2a_invocation_service --> A2ARoutingException : invalid route / method
A2AJsonRpcClient --> DownstreamA2AException : downstream A2A failure
llm_supervisor_planning_service --> SupervisorChatProcessingException : plan/review parse failure
llm_supervisor_response_compose_service --> SupervisorChatProcessingException : compose failure
supervisor_agent_orchestrator --> RuntimeError : state/persistence mismatch
supervisor_a2a_endpoint --> ValueError : validator / params
supervisor_a2a_endpoint --> JSONDecodeError : invalid JSON
A2AJsonRpcClient --> HttpxHTTPError : upstream HTTP failure

supervisor_exception_handler --> ChatProcessingException : exception mapping
supervisor_exception_handler --> Exception : name-based mapping\nA2ARoutingException / DownstreamA2AException /\nSupervisorChatProcessingException
supervisor_exception_handler --> ValueError : exception mapping
supervisor_exception_handler --> RuntimeError : exception mapping
supervisor_exception_handler --> HttpxHTTPError : exception mapping
supervisor_exception_handler --> JSONDecodeError : exception mapping

note bottom of supervisor_exception_handler
Return sanitized response
- /a2a/** -> JsonRpcResponse(error)
- non-A2A -> ErrorResponse
- no downstream raw body/header leak
- many JSON-RPC validation errors are returned directly by endpoint/validator without throwing
end note
@enduml
